I Tried Where Winds Meet

Make sure to download Where Winds Meet on Steam using https://bit.ly/4r2XDNK You can check out their full website using https://bit.ly/4p3TNlt. Thanks to Where Winders Meet for sponsoring the video!

In this video, I played Where Winds Meet and will showcase my early gameplay experiences with the game. Enjoy the video and let me know what you think!
